title: 1962 Ohio State Buckeyes football team
text:
The 1962 Ohio State Buckeyes football team represented the <a href="Ohio%20State%20University">Ohio State University</a> in the <a href="1962%20Big%20Ten%20Conference%20football%20season">1962 Big Ten Conference football season</a>. The Buckeyes compiled a 6–3 record.
